{"id": "ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 95, "displayName": {"text": "Shoe Palace", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Retail chain selling athletic shoes, streetwear & accessories for adults & children.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wRk5HOUdObkJ2UlRac1ltTjJjVmxrTVhkRUxWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The vibe in this place is soooo…\nA super well-thought-out concept, every corner of the room is thought out\nThe stuff is so polite and very attentive", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The vibe in this place is soooo…\nA super well-thought-out concept, every corner of the room is thought out\nThe stuff is so polite and very attentive", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Индира Айдарханова", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101010609593902353138/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSptYFsC0xgGWlXZlfw8qeH5iSHsaAfwOrJ_QxWI2BD7avia0z=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-21T23:59:27.393249705Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wRk5HOUdObkJ2UlRac1ltTjJjVmxrTVhkRUxWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wRk5HOUdObkJ2UlRac1ltTjJjVmxrTVhkRUxWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c6480706aaab:0x7ca5eecb92da6ae8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213NFRuUjVRMjB5YUdkemVXdHlMVWRaZURaVlgxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "First time shopping at shoe palace and let me tell you, this location is awesome. Literally from the manager (she was great) to the security guard were nothing but friendly and helpful! Thanks to the young man that rung me out and chopped it up with me about the shoes I had just purchased.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "First time shopping at shoe palace and let me tell you, this location is awesome. Literally from the manager (she was great) to the security guard were nothing but friendly and helpful! Thanks to the young man that rung me out and chopped it up with me about the shoes I had just purchased.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "jeremy santillana", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109852860948132656563/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhCDuhRPML1ddAT0Qx6qnfS3ducvSyvNTT0ud3WyNEWrRcNQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-15T19:39:41.706093537Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213NFRuUjVRMjB5YUdkemVXdHlMVWRaZURaVlgxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT213NFRuUjVRMjB5YUdkemVXdHlMVWRaZURaVlgxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c6480706aaab:0x7ca5eecb92da6ae8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM5cktidTJ3RRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "This is one of my favorite Shoe Palace’s\n\nI’ve bought other shoes here in the past and it was a smooth transaction.  I might of waited a while because it was a hot release but it was the normal expectation.\n\nThe location has lots of different shoes from different brands and the presentation is phenomenal. The arcade is a nice touch and customer service there has been very helpful.\n\nI’d definitely come back here again and get other drops in the future.\n\n***Update***\nI recently went after the renovation and it’s definitely way better. I also got a pair of the sold out everywhere Jordan flu games!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "This is one of my favorite Shoe Palace’s\n\nI’ve bought other shoes here in the past and it was a smooth transaction.  I might of waited a while because it was a hot release but it was the normal expectation.\n\nThe location has lots of different shoes from different brands and the presentation is phenomenal. The arcade is a nice touch and customer service there has been very helpful.\n\nI’d definitely come back here again and get other drops in the future.\n\n***Update***\nI recently went after the renovation and it’s definitely way better. I also got a pair of the sold out everywhere Jordan flu games!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "funning", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110827233308643416287/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8eBl2cEQrW_I0wLzkTGJfbzU3l3DVtdSN1SSpmiH9IiBxJ8s=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba7"}, "publishTime": "2025-04-06T18:06:33.369288Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM5cktidTJ3RRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUM5cktidTJ3RRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c6480706aaab:0x7ca5eecb92da6ae8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xjeGFURXdiVWR6VDJWMmNUQjBibDkxYkRSU1NIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "The store is beautiful but our salesperson, who walks the shoes up to the register, only put ONE SHOE IN THE BOX. $200 Timberlands. We live 45 miles away. The store is not answering the phones. I have left an email for corporate and I will update once we see how they plan to handle this debacle.  Gorgeous location aside, it means nothing if you don’t get the shoes home with you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The store is beautiful but our salesperson, who walks the shoes up to the register, only put ONE SHOE IN THE BOX. $200 Timberlands. We live 45 miles away. The store is not answering the phones. I have left an email for corporate and I will update once we see how they plan to handle this debacle.  Gorgeous location aside, it means nothing if you don’t get the shoes home with you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Niki W.", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110933868566195704527/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLucWUxy_I4-3MZfQSoiNbSP_c0dI009NT3sBNurMv6t7A7GA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-29T03:12:57.649843078Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xjeGFURXdiVWR6VDJWMmNUQjBibDkxYkRSU1NIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xjeGFURXdiVWR6VDJWMmNUQjBibDkxYkRSU1NIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c6480706aaab:0x7ca5eecb92da6ae8"}, {"name": "places/ChIJq6oGB0jGwoAR6GraksvupXw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Gak5WUnNVRVJ1TVRKdVdGZEdNMGd0UmxwUkxYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "If you planning on ordering online with SP I recommend you don’t. Their Processing  time is ridiculous better off ordering from FLocker or somewhere else", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "If you planning on ordering online with SP I recommend you don’t. Their Processing  time is ridiculous better off ordering from FLocker or somewhere else", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Joshua Segovia", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118390509287272751928/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIn_RwwYMpgNs5pqU-zQZ6ttOhnzGJhuA8aFeOsc1FFmbUVPg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-19T19:11:53.066752823Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25Gak5WUnNVRVJ1TVRKdVdGZEdNMGd0UmxwUkxYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2